title.newValue: Outlook: Microsoft Feed on the Outlook Mobile Search Page

description.newValue:
The Search Page in Outlook Mobile is being enhanced with a new Feed that aims to help users stay on top of interesting things that are happening in Microsoft 365. The Feed looks at what is happening in Microsoft 365 and surfaces updates and insights about people, documents, and other artifacts in a vertical Feed view, ranked personally for each user.
GA date: June CY2022
